### Test Quick Task Creation Endpoint
### Make sure to replace {{baseUrl}} and {{authToken}} with actual values

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@authToken = your-jwt-token-here

### 1. Create Quick Task - Basic (Only Title)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/quick
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "title": "Buy groceries"
}

### 2. Create Quick Task - With Description
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/quick
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "title": "Complete project documentation",
  "description": "Add API documentation, test cases, and deployment guide"
}

### 3. Test Validation Error - Empty Title
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/quick
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "title": ""
}

### 4. Test Validation Error - Missing Title
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/quick
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "description": "Some description without title"
}

### 5. Test Unauthenticated Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/quick
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "This should fail"
}

### 6. Get Tasks by Board (to verify task was created)
### Replace {{boardId}} with actual board ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/by-board/{{boardId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
